{"tid":2399744,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"文匯大公接連指控大律師公會主席夏博義 勾結美國CIA危害國家安全以及曾發表文章支持藏獨","createTime":"2021-02-08T11:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T13:03:16.000Z","uid":292499,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"66b9d3a60da3ebe946baa1bbc0acee790f5c3238","tid":2399744,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:26:45.000Z","msg":"上月當選大律師公會主席的資深大律師夏博義，繼續被中共喉舌攻擊，中聯辦控制的《文匯報》、《大公報》和《香港商報》，今日（8 日）發文「狙擊」，指控夏博義擔任首任主席的「香港人權監察」，與「美國國家民主基金會」（NED）關係密切，又稱人權監察接受其資助，從事反對 23 條立法、跟進反送中運動警暴等，又指控夏博義本人曾發文支持「藏獨」。報道又指夏博義在擔任大律師公會主席前，曾任英國自由民主黨牛津市議員，而該黨「支持香港黑暴」。《商報》則刊登「評論」，指大律師公會不應該政治化，有「意見」認為大律師公會應宣誓擁護基本法，效忠香港特區，有關建議「值得研究」。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n《文匯報》報道並且介紹，夏博義在 90 年代與公會前主席戴啟思、港大法律學院教授陳文敏共同成立「香港人權監察」，並出任首任主席；報道又稱「香港人權監察」與「美國國家民主基金會」（NED）關係密切，NED 在 10 多年間向人權監察撥款近 1,500 萬。報道形容，NED 是美國中情局「顛覆他國政權的『白手套』」<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n報道又批評夏博義，在 2013 年曾經發表「藏獨」文章，指西藏有「民族自決權」，並指西藏是「處於外來軍事統治下的國家」。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/左報續狙擊夏博義-指控曾發文撐藏獨-所屬英國政黨撐-黑暴/?fbclid=IwAR0aXlL5mxAZj7qwPu2PeGHYJacNM2ZzlCUZSZLaGpFOMAK5IsjTxmpB41U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%B7%A6%E5%A0%B1%E7%BA%8C%E7%8B%99%E6%93%8A%E5%A4%8F%E5%8D%9A%E7%BE%A9-%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E6%9B%BE%E7%99%BC%E6%96%87%E6%92%90%E8%97%8F%E7%8D%A8-%E6%89%80%E5%B1%AC%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E9%BB%A8%E6%92%90-%E9%BB%91%E6%9A%B4%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0aXlL5mxAZj7qwPu2PeGHYJacNM2ZzlCUZSZLaGpFOMAK5IsjTxmpB41U&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUijBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=074c9ee5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E5%B7%A6%E5%A0%B1%E7%BA%8C%E7%8B%99%E6%93%8A%E5%A4%8F%E5%8D%9A%E7%BE%A9-%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E6%9B%BE%E7%99%BC%E6%96%87%E6%92%90%E8%97%8F%E7%8D%A8-%E6%89%80%E5%B1%AC%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E9%BB%A8%E6%92%90-%E9%BB%91%E6%9A%B4%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0aXlL5mxAZj7qwPu2PeGHYJacNM2ZzlCUZSZLaGpFOMAK5IsjTxmpB41U&h=b37a7929\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/左報續狙擊夏博義-指控曾發文撐藏獨-所屬英國政黨撐-黑暴/?fbclid=IwAR0aXlL5mxAZj7qwPu2PeGHYJacNM2ZzlCUZSZLaGpFOMAK5IsjTxmpB41U</a>"},{"pid":"b0dda536ef761b650d19bb004e508be9b97d5904","tid":2399744,"uid":57513,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:29:14.000Z","msg":"有問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b0913c7a225e4855827781f0663d955e9134eb","tid":2399744,"uid":292499,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:29:58.000Z","msg":"CIA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d42ac192da87cc47e7b39ab10e2a1a1d4b59485","tid":2399744,"uid":292499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />吹到"},{"pid":"711ed101db8cde632538b2545d3308c65f821b3f","tid":2399744,"uid":292499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:30:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eff26e4e01a167edc7834b568930bc901726863","tid":2399744,"uid":292499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T11:31:31.000Z","msg":"屈到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d8632b